title: United Kingdom Imports - Tools, Cutlery, Spoons & Forks, Of Base Metal
description: Imports - Tools, Cutlery, Spoons & Forks, Of Base Metal in the United Kingdom decreased to 125.85 GBP Million in September from 136.81 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Tools, Cutlery, Spoons & Forks, Of Base in the United Kingdom averaged 111.63 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1763.31 GBP Million in April of 2015 and a record low of 68.94 GBP Million in December of 2004. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of ols, Cutlery, Spoons & Forks, of Base M.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
